{"tid":1469691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中方要求聯合國停止干預香港事務","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:31:43.000Z","uid":41343,"like":8,"dislike":442,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"e56a08b19561d85ae7c5762b35fc4666d4d1f016","tid":1469691,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:44:29.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港示威活動持續，聯合國早前促請港府獨立調查警方發射催淚彈的方式，有否違反國際規範，中方反駁指聯合國向暴力示威者發出錯誤訊息，要求停止干預香港事務。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐日內瓦的聯合國代表團發出聲明，反駁人權事務高級專員辦公室，形容激進暴徒故意延續暴力，破壞香港公共設施，癱瘓機場運作和使用致命武器，有轉向恐怖主義的趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n辦公室質疑警方行動是向暴力示威者發出錯誤信息，要求停止干預香港事務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%8D%E9%A7%81%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%90%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%99%BC%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF-014736627.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%25A7%2581%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2590%2591%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%258C%25AF%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2581%25AF-014736627.html&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0RPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=adf99a44\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%8D%E9%A7%81%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%90%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%99%BC%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF-014736627.html</a>"},{"pid":"485c981a8bb4c98044ab48424b34c49daf5f506e","tid":1469691,"uid":254745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28abd2d1973a5c7dca8369e9a03508fd6555a0f","tid":1469691,"uid":12179,"like":415,"dislike":0,"score":415,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:47:21.000Z","msg":"原來中國已退出聯合國？"},{"pid":"f9315